data.description: Come, see this well appointed single story home, located in the picturesque community of Palisades. The home offers open living areas for easy entertaining. Upon entering the home, there is a tile area with a large coat closet and a half wall, which separates the entry from the living area. As you leave the entryway, you will be greeted by a formal living room and dining room space. Directly behind the formal living area you’ll find the kitchen. Any chef would be pleased with the double door, pantry, and plenty of counter space for meal prep. At the end of the center island there is a built-in wine rack. The kitchen flows directly into the great room. There is a screened in porch off the back of the house where you can enjoy meals or just curl up in a comfy chair and take in the beautiful Florida weather. The owners retreat sits off the back of the house as well, and has its own private door to access the screen porch. This retreat offers a spa, like bathroom with a walk in shower and garden tub. Are you a shopper? No need to worry about your shoe collection. The Owner’s Retreat features an oversized walk-in closet! This home is conveniently located close  to Florida theme parks, golf courses, shopping and restaurants. Scedule your appointment today to see all it has to offer!
